{{infobox country at games | NOC = BEN | NOCname = [[Benin National Olympic and Sports Committee]] | games = Summer Olympics | year = 2004 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = | location = [[Athens]] | competitors = '''4''' | sports = 2 | flagbearer = [[Fabienne Feraez]] | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }}
'''[[Benin]]''' competed at the '''[[2004 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Athens]], [[Greece]], from 13 to 29 August 2004.
