The '''Federação Maranhense de Futebol''' ([[English language|English]]: Football Association of Maranhão state) was founded on January 11, 1918, and it manages all the official [[association football|football]] tournaments within the state of [[Maranhão]], which are the [[Campeonato Maranhense]], the [[Campeonato Maranhense (lower levels)|Campeonato Maranhense lower levels]] and the [[Copa União do Maranhão]], and represents the clubs at the [[Brazilian Football Confederation|Brazilian Football Confederation (CBF)]].

