{{EngvarB|date=March 2017}} {{Use dmy dates|date=March 2017}} {{Unreferenced|date=February 2007}} {{Infobox Sport governing body |assocname= Gibraltar Cycling Association |logo= |sport= [[bicycle racing|Cycle racing]] |abbrev = GCA |founded = |aff = [[British Cycling]] |affdate = |region = [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]] |regionyear = |president = |secretary = |coach = |womenscoach = |url = |countryflag= Gibraltar }} The '''Gibraltar Cycling Association''' is the [[Sport governing body|governing body]] for [[bicycle racing]] in the [[British overseas territories|British overseas territory]] of [[Gibraltar]].
The national governing body for the territory is [[British Cycling]] in the [[United Kingdom]].
