{{Infobox football club | clubname = Guyana Defence Force FC | image = Guyana Defense Force.svg | image_size = 200px | fullname = Guyana Defence Force Football Department FC | nickname = ''Defence Force, GDF Football Club'' | founded = 1965 | ground = [[Guyana Defence Force Ground]] | capacity = | chrtitle = President | chairman = {{Flagicon|GUY}} [[David A. Granger]] | mgrtitle = Manager | manager = | league = [[GFF Elite League]] | season = [[GFF Elite League|2016–17]] | position = 1st | current = | website = }}
'''Guyana Defence Force FC''', colloquially known simply as '''Defence Force''' is a [[Guyana|Guyanese]] football club based in [[Georgetown, Guyana|Georgetown]], competing in the [[GFF Elite League]], the top tier of Guyanese football. The club is fielded by the nation's [[Guyana Defence Force|defence force]] and military.
