{{Infobox organization | name = Turkish Cricket Board | image = Turkish Cricket Board.PNG | size = 125px | caption = | motto = | formation = 2008 | headquarters = [[Ankara]], [[Turkey]] | membership = [[International Cricket Council]] | leader_title = [[Chairman]] | leader_name = Dr. Hayri Ozkan | key_people = Dr. Syed F. Mahmud (Chief Executive Officer) | website = [http://www.bilkent.edu.tr/~cricket/ bilkent.edu.tr] }}
The '''Turkish Cricket Board''' is the official [[Sport governing body|governing body]] of the sport of [[cricket]] in [[Turkey]]. It is Turkey's representative at the [[International Cricket Council]] and is an affiliate member and has been a member of that body since 2008. It is also a member of the [[European Cricket Council]].
